The paper proposes a deep learning approach for constructing projections of high-dimensional data, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and data science. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the computational efficiency and stability of the proposed method, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of neural networks and machine learning (cs.NE) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
